(8, '28', NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: -42.5pt; margin: 0cm 2cm 0pt; tab-stops: 35.4pt 70.8pt 106.2pt 158.25pt;\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt;\">Mossor&oacute; (RN), 23 de Novembro de 2011.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 2cm 0pt; tab-stops: 35.4pt 70.8pt 106.2pt 158.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"padding-bottom: 1pt; padding-left: 11pt; padding-right: 4pt; background: #e6e6e6; margin-left: 2cm; margin-right: 2cm; padding-top: 1pt; mso-element: para-border-div; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; border: windowtext 1pt solid;\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background: #e6e6e6; tab-stops: 35.4pt 70.8pt 106.2pt 158.25pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-outline-level: 1; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 11.0pt; padding: 0cm;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt;\">INFORMATIVO</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background: #e6e6e6; tab-stops: 35.4pt 70.8pt 106.2pt 158.25pt; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-outline-level: 1; mso-padding-alt: 1.0pt 4.0pt 1.0pt 11.0pt; padding: 0cm;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt;\">ASSEMBL&Eacute;IA DE <span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>22/11/11</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0cm 2cm 0pt; tab-stops: 35.4pt 70.8pt 106.2pt 158.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0cm 2cm 0pt; tab-stops: 35.4pt 70.8pt 106.2pt 158.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 7.1pt; margin: 0cm 2cm 0pt; tab-stops: 312.75pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0cm 2cm 0pt; tab-stops: 35.4pt 70.8pt 106.2pt 158.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt;\">Prezados Cond&ocirc;minos</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0cm 2cm 0pt; tab-stops: 35.4pt 70.8pt 106.2pt 158.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0cm 2cm 0pt; tab-stops: 35.4pt 70.8pt 106.2pt 158.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt;\">Vimos atrav&eacute;s deste informar que na Assembl&eacute;ia realizada na data de ontem ficaram deliberados e aprovados os seguintes pontos:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0cm 2cm 0pt; tab-stops: 35.4pt 70.8pt 106.2pt 158.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0cm 2cm 0pt; tab-stops: 35.4pt 70.8pt 106.2pt 158.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0cm 2cm 0pt; tab-stops: 35.4pt 70.8pt 106.2pt 158.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt;\">01) <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Energia Trifasica:</span></strong> Foi deliberado aprovado a solicita&ccedil;&atilde;o de or&ccedil;amento do projeto<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>de execu&ccedil;&atilde;o, dos materiais e servi&ccedil;os e deliberar em uma pr&oacute;xima assembl&eacute;ia.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0cm 2cm 0pt; tab-stops: 35.4pt 70.8pt 106.2pt 158.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0cm 2cm 0pt; tab-stops: 35.4pt 70.8pt 106.2pt 158.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt;\">02) <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Lombadas e estacionamento</span></strong>: foi rejeitada a implanta&ccedil;&atilde;o das lombadas no condom&iacute;nio e aprovado a<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>confec&ccedil;&atilde;o de uma placa de sinaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o de velocidade, com dimens&otilde;es<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>maiores para o port&atilde;o e multar a unidade infratora que trafegar acima do limite permitido e estacionar o ve&iacute;culo na rua ou em cima das cal&ccedil;adas do condom&iacute;nio.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0cm 2cm 0pt; tab-stops: 35.4pt 70.8pt 106.2pt 158.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0cm 2cm 0pt; tab-stops: 35.4pt 70.8pt 106.2pt 158.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt;\">03) <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Abertura e fechamento do port&atilde;o a noite</span></strong>: Foi deliberado e aprovado que dever&aacute; ser feita pelo porteiro ap&oacute;s identificar o morador que devera acender a luz interna do veiculo e se<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>necess&aacute;rio abaixar o vidro e s&oacute; ap&oacute;s este procedimento ser&aacute; liberada a entrada.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0cm 2cm 0pt; tab-stops: 35.4pt 70.8pt 106.2pt 158.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0cm 2cm 0pt; tab-stops: 35.4pt 70.8pt 106.2pt 158.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt;\">04) <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Fossa ,</span></strong> foi deliberado e aprovado convidar para uma assembl&eacute;ia a Engenheira Sanit&aacute;ria Dra. Renata . que dever&aacute; explicar e esclarecer todos as duvidas com rela&ccedil;&atilde;o ao problema.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0cm 2cm 0pt; tab-stops: 35.4pt 70.8pt 106.2pt 158.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0cm 2cm 0pt; tab-stops: 35.4pt 70.8pt 106.2pt 158.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt;\">05) <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Animais</span></strong> ; O sindico salientou que alguns animais est&atilde;o circulando pela &aacute;rea comum do cond&ocirc;mino e em algumas casas , o que &eacute; proibido em conven&ccedil;&atilde;o , solicitou<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>aten&ccedil;&atilde;o dos propriet&aacute;rios destes animais, pois ser&atilde;o notificados e multados caso continuem a<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>ocorrer estes fatos. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0cm 2cm 0pt; tab-stops: 35.4pt 70.8pt 106.2pt 158.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0cm 2cm 0pt; tab-stops: 35.4pt 70.8pt 106.2pt 158.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '2011-11-23', '1'),
