rong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: black;\">Local:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: black;\"> No Condom&iacute;nio. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 125%;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: black;\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Convocamos os cond&ocirc;minos do Residencial Ot&aacute;vio Ferreira &ndash; Condom&iacute;nio II para a Assembl&eacute;ia do Condom&iacute;nio que se realizar&aacute; na data, hor&aacute;rio, e local acima indicado, para discutirem e deliberarem a seguinte ordem do dia:</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"> </span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0cm; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: 14.2pt list 36.0pt;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: black;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">1)<span style=\"font: 7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span></span></span></em></strong><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: black;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>Delibera&ccedil;&atilde;o e orienta&ccedil;&atilde;o para a utiliza&ccedil;&atilde;o do sistema de g&aacute;s central e retirada dos botij&otilde;es das unidades</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">,<strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"> (qu&oacute;rum maioria simples )</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; tab-stops: 14.2pt;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0cm; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: 14.2pt list 36.0pt;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: black;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">2)<span style=\"font: 7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span></span></span></em></strong><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: black;\">Delibera&ccedil;&atilde;o e Aprova&ccedil;&atilde;o de taxa extra para reforma e adequa&ccedil;&atilde;o das guaritas para melhor seguran&ccedil;a e para colocar<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>gerador de energia(</span></strong><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">qu&oacute;rum maioria simples )</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0cm; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: 14.2pt list 36.0pt;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: black;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">3)<span style=\"font: 7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span></span></span></em></strong><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: black;\">Delibera&ccedil;&atilde;o e aprova&ccedil;&atilde;o de taxa extra para aquisi&ccedil;&atilde;o de rel&oacute;gios medidores de g&aacute;s (qu&oacute;rum maioria simples)</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; tab-stops: 14.2pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Os representantes de cond&ocirc;minos (propriet&aacute;rios) dever&atilde;o apresentar procura&ccedil;&atilde;o, onde inquilinos s&oacute; poder&atilde;o votar mediante procura&ccedil;&atilde;o. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: black;\">Conforme inciso III, do artigo 1335 do C&oacute;digo Civil Brasileiro, somente poder&aacute; participar, e votar, os cond&ocirc;minos que estiverem em dia com suas contribui&ccedil;&otilde;es condominiais (adimplentes). </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: black;\">Salientamos, que conforme a Lei do inquilinato &eacute; obriga&ccedil;&atilde;o do inquilino a entrega desta convoca&ccedil;&atilde;o aos propriet&aacute;rios, onde a mesma encontra-se na portaria; As decis&otilde;es se tornar&atilde;o obrigat&oacute;rias, inclusive aos ausentes.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Agradecendo o vosso comparecimento, subscrevo atenciosamente,</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Gladstone Morais de Noronha</span></strong><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\">Sindico</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoFootnoteText\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</p>', '2013-12-03', '1'),
(14, '80', NULL, '<p><strong>PREZADOS COND&Ocirc;MINOS,</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>INFORMAMOS QUE O AGENDAMENTO DE MUDAN&Ccedil;A SERA LIBERADO AP&Oacute;S DETERMINA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O DA CONSTRUTORA. ONDE TODOS SER&Atilde;O COMUNICADOS E RECEBER&Atilde;O TODA ORIENTA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O VIA E-MAIL&nbsp;E ATRAVES DO &nbsp;SITE. </strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>AGRADECEMOS A ATEN&Ccedil;&Atilde;O. </strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>CORDIALMENTE </strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>A ADMINISTRA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O</strong></p>', '2014-06-03', '1'),
